---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Decision Intelligence Platform | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Integrated modelling, scenario analysis, and decision-support systems for complex policy, infrastructure, and investment decisions."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Decision Intelligence Platform
      </p>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Integrated intelligence for complex decisions.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        The Decision Intelligence Platform helps organisations combine evidence, models, data, and expert judgement into structured decision-support systems.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The problem
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Important decisions rarely depend on one dataset or one model.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Public agencies, infrastructure providers, regulators, and investors often need to evaluate options under uncertainty. The evidence can span economic models, spatial data, forecasts, technical reports, consultation material, and institutional knowledge.
          </p>
          <p>
            The Decision Intelligence Platform provides a structured environment for bringing these inputs together so teams can explore options, understand trade-offs, and make decisions that are clearer, faster, and more defensible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          What it supports
        </p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Decision support built around evidence, scenarios, and consequences.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Option assessment</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Compare policy, investment, and operational choices using structured evidence and analytical criteria.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Scenario analysis</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Explore how outcomes may change under different assumptions, future conditions, and intervention pathways.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Trade-off analysis</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Identify distributional, economic, spatial, financial, and operational trade-offs across options.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Decision reporting</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Generate structured summaries that support advice, governance papers, business cases, and reviews.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Example applications
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Designed for decisions where evidence and consequences matter.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Infrastructure investment prioritisation and option assessment.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Climate adaptation, resilience, and transition planning.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Policy evaluation, regulatory analysis, and impact assessment.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Spatial, economic, and distributional decision support.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI connected to modelling, economics, and domain expertise.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            The platform is not designed as a generic dashboard or chatbot. It is designed as a decision-support layer that connects AI with models, datasets, reporting workflows, and professional judgement.
          </p>
          <p>
            PrincipalAI draws on Principal Economics’ experience in economic appraisal, infrastructure, transport, energy, climate, health, regulation, and applied modelling.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Build decision intelligence around your most important choices.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about decision-support systems for policy, infrastructure, climate, regulation, and investment.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
